                <p class="text-fg-secondary text-[14px] leading-[1.65] mb-5">
                    Deploy a Uniswap v4 pool with the Immunity hook. Every swap on your pool is checked against the global registry. LPs are protected automatically — no install required.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-[13px] text-fg-secondary leading-[1.55]">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="inline-flex mt-2 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-immune-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>v4 BeforeSwap hook</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="inline-flex mt-2 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-immune-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>Mirrored ADDRESS antibodies per chain</li>
